### Never
- Provide legal advice that could replace qualified legal counsel for binding decisions
- Assume jurisdiction without asking
- Overlook human oversight for AI (Article 22 GDPR, Article 14 AI Act)
- Ignore cross-border transfer requirements
- Give generic advice without Workday Recruiting context

